{"type": "article", "id": 23936, "title": "珠宝包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-16T07:00:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 96, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071743026SgCVYTsBrzXnJAy.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">Atoll Gozde 是土耳其设计师 Yasemin Gözde 自已的珠宝品牌，包装则来自香港的设计公司 Frames。包装本身的外形很普通，只是选用了少见的墨绿色作为底色，搭配棕色的盒子内衬，给人森林和自然的印象。在文字部分则用金色来提亮，排在正中间或者上下地方，很古典。包装盒上可以看到细密的花纹，以指向珠宝本身的精致。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060717430040zYflEJAORI2uLQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174300rK2ouXx6YVq5we1Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071743002EJn8wKM4sxyNV6q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071743011vHuhFt9iybqsWfg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174302I4Q2AmJ7oZd6V01x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}